cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper deals with computer vision and image processing techniques for scene background initialization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for image analysis, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the evaluation of different methods, which could be related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, since the paper deals with video surveillance, it could also be related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
